<div class="login-div-02"></div>
<div class="login-div-03">
<div class="chip-glass-inline">
<span class="icon-ms-sm-white">verified</span>
<span class="login-span-01">신뢰받는 여행 플랫폼</span>
</div>
</div>
<div class="login-div-04">
<h1 class="login-h1-01">여행의 모든 순간을<br/>함께하세요</h1>
<p class="login-p-01">새로운 경험과 추억이 기다리고 있습니다.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="auth-form-column">
<div class="mb-8">
<h2 class="login-h2-01">로그인</h2>
<p class="calendar-add-event-span-02">계정에 로그인하여 서비스를 이용하세요.</p>
</div>
<form class="login-form-01" action="/login" method="post">
<label class="fx-group-col-gap2">
<span class="login-span-02">
                            이메일
                            <span class="text-danger">*</span>
</span>
<div class="is-relative">
<div class="login-div-05">
<span class="icon-ms-20">mail</span>
</div>
<input class="signup-input-solid" placeholder="name@example.com" type="email" name="email" value=""/>
</div>
</label>
<label class="fx-group-col-gap2">
<div class="login-div-06">
<span class="login-span-02">
